    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><anchor id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md51"/> </para>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md52">
<title>复数四则运算</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>重载运算符，支持 double、Rational、BigInt。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：按复数实部/虚部分别运算。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：支持符号混合。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>局限：复数轨迹、复方程求根未完善。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md53">
<title>极坐标/指数形式</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>支持 to_complex()、to_double() 转换。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：模长与角度转换，指数形式 e^(iθ)。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：支持符号角度。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>局限：高阶复数变换未支持。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md54">
<title>to_symbolic()</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>转换为符号表达式。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：构造 <ref refid="dc/d25/classSymbolicExpr" kindref="compound">SymbolicExpr</ref> 节点。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：支持符号化简。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>局限：复杂嵌套下效率低。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md55">
<title>to_double()</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>数值化。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：实部/虚部转 double。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：支持高精度。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>局限：精度损失。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md56">
<title>to_string()</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>格式化输出。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：按实部/虚部格式化字符串。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：支持符号输出。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>局限：复杂嵌套下格式化有限。 </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect1 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md57">
<title>复数模块</title>
<para>主要头文件：<computeroutput><ref refid="d4/d49/irrational_8hpp" kindref="compound">include/irrational.hpp</ref></computeroutput>、<computeroutput><ref refid="d6/dda/value_8hpp" kindref="compound">include/value.hpp</ref></computeroutput></para>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md58">
<title>Irrational</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>复数/无理数类型，支持模长、共轭、极坐标转换。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>算法：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>四则运算：重载运算符，支持 double、Rational、BigInt。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>极坐标/指数形式：to_complex()、to_double() 支持转换。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>特性：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>支持复数表达式与符号化简。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>支持复数与符号混合运算。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>已知问题：<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>复数轨迹、复方程求根未完善。</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="d0/d9b/md_docs_2modules_2complex_1autotoc_md59">
<title>主要函数</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>to_symbolic()</computeroutput>：转换为符号表达式。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>to_double()</computeroutput>：数值化。</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>to_string()</computeroutput>：格式化输出。 </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
